==CP==
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! COMMAND !! DESCRIPTION !! EXAMPLE
|-
| I CMS || Enter into CMS || 
|-
| IPL NUMBER || IPL from NUMBER || IPL 150
|-
| CP SET RUN ON || Maintain VM running when disconnecting from z/VM ||
|}

==Linux==
* To run CP commands from Linux while in the x3270 session, type: #CP COMMAND, for example, #CP SYSTEM CLEAR. This would stop the VM.


